ClineContinue <p>Install Cline, then add to its MCP settings: <pre><code>{
  "mcpServers": {
    "pm-skills": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["pm-skills-mcp"]
    }
  }
}
</code></pre></p> <p>Install Continue, then edit <code>~/.continue/config.json</code>: <pre><code>{
  "mcpServers": [
    {
      "name": "pm-skills",
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["pm-skills-mcp"]
    }
  ]
}
</code></pre></p>
